room_title: Escape room "Escape the Naughty List" by Escape Room Adventure in Daytona Beach
room_address: 388 S Atlantic Ave Ormond Beach, FL 32176
room_description: ​​You and your friends have found out that your names are mistakenly on the naughty list! Now you must find a way to remove your names or you will be stuck with a stocking full of coal on Christmas morning! After some research, you have discovered that Santa goes out at the same time each day for an hour long walk. You will have one hour to break into his house - find the list and erase your names before he gets back!
